09:49.130 --> 09:52.633
salad, a tangerine,

09:52.675 --> 09:54.635
and, ooh, Jordan almonds.

09:54.677 --> 09:56.096
What do you have?

09:56.137 --> 09:58.639
Leftover eggs

09:56.137 --> 09:58.639
from breakfast.

09:58.681 --> 10:00.434
Oh.

10:00.475 --> 10:03.270
Uh, I'm on a special diet,

10:00.475 --> 10:03.270
