10:03.311 --> 10:05.688
Oh, I forgot.

10:05.730 --> 10:07.648
I have to go...

10:05.730 --> 10:07.648
work out.

10:07.690 --> 10:09.609
I'll see you later.

10:12.070 --> 10:14.030
I can't take

10:12.070 --> 10:14.030
this anymore!

10:14.072 --> 10:16.157
Everything I want,

10:14.072 --> 10:16.157
I can't have!

10:16.199 --> 10:17.700
Anything that's nice,

10:16.199 --> 10:17.700
I can't do!

10:17.742 --> 10:20.828
Everyone in the world

10:17.742 --> 10:20.828
gets to do everything except me!

10:20.870 --> 10:23.039
Malcolm...

10:20.870 --> 10:23.039
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

10:23.081 --> 10:24.665
I know there's other people

10:23.081 --> 10:24.665
worse off than me.

10:24.707 --> 10:26.667
You know what?

10:24.707 --> 10:26.667
I don't care.

10:26.709 --> 10:29.546
I'm sick of going to school

10:26.709 --> 10:29.546
