10:29.588 --> 10:30.964
Malcolm...

10:31.005 --> 10:32.507
I hate being poor, okay?!

10:32.549 --> 10:33.674
I mean, is that so bad?

10:33.716 --> 10:36.052
Why is that, like,

10:33.716 --> 10:36.052
