10:48.815 --> 10:51.568
before  you start talking.

10:48.815 --> 10:51.568
Yeah.

10:52.735 --> 10:54.154
Francis, where have you been?

10:54.195 --> 10:55.989
I've been looking for you

10:54.195 --> 10:55.989
